Glossary
Abbreviations used in table:
METAL: MEdian Time Average Lead.
Median of time average leads for each game played by a team.

TALE: Time Average Lead Evaluation
Average of time averaged leads for each game played by a team, adjusted for opponent quality (TALE SOS).
TALE - TALE SOS = raw time average lead for regular season games played

TALE SOS: Time Average Lead Evaluation Strength of Schedule
Average of opponents time average leads against other NFL teams

AVG +/-: Aggregate point differential for team, on per game basis
(Season Points Scored - Season Points Allowed)/Games Played
